posts.post_title: WTB: Semi-Rare back ungraded t206 in decent shape for a good price
posts.post_content: I’m looking for some semi-rare backed t206 ungraded cards. I will also accept graded if you can come below my price range of $300. If you have anything you’d like to get rid of you can email at me [url]fisher29norris@gmail.com[/url]
